name: Object Relational Mapper
description: PHP object relational mapper (ORM) that sits on top of a powerful database abstraction layer (DBAL). One of its key features is the option to write database queries in a proprietary object oriented SQL dialect called Doctrine Query Language (DQL). This provides developers with a powerful alternative to SQL that maintains flexibility without requiring unnecessary code duplication.

name: Database Abstraction Layer
description: Powerful PHP database abstraction layer (DBAL) with many features for database schema introspection and management.

name: MongoDB Object Document Mapper
description: PHP Doctrine MongoDB Object Document Mapper (ODM) provides transparent persistence for PHP objects to MongoDB.

name: PHPCR ODM
description: PHP Doctrine Content Repository Object Document Mapper (ODM) provides transparent persistence for PHP objects.

name: CouchDB Object Document Mapper
description: PHP Doctrine CouchDB Object Document Mapper (ODM) provides transparent persistence for PHP objects to CouchDB.

name: Migrations
description: PHP Doctrine Migrations project offer additional functionality on top of the database abstraction layer (DBAL) for versioning your database schema and easily deploying changes to it. It is a very easy to use and a powerful tool.

name: Common
description: PHP Doctrine Common project is a library that provides additional functionality that other Doctrine projects depend on such as better reflection support, persistence interfaces, proxies, event system and much more.

name: MongoDB Abstraction Layer
description: PHP Doctrine MongoDB project is a library that provides a wrapper around the native PHP Mongo PECL extension to provide additional functionality.

name: OrientDB Object Document Mapper
description: PHP OrientDB Object Document Mapper (ODM) provides transparent persistence for PHP objects to OrientDB.

name: Annotations
description: PHP Doctrine DocBlock Annotations Parser library that lets you parse structured data out of PHP docblocks for use with other functionality.

name: Collections
description: PHP Doctrine Collections library that adds additional functionality on top of PHP arrays.

name: Inflector
description: PHP Doctrine Inflector is a small library that can perform string manipulations with regard to upper/lowercase and singular/plural forms of words.

name: Cache
description: PHP Doctrine Cache library is a popular cache implementation that supports many different drivers such as redis, memcache, apc, mongodb and others.

name: Lexer
description: PHP Doctrine Lexer parser library that can be used in Top-Down, Recursive Descent Parsers.

name: Event Manager
description: The Doctrine Event Manager is a simple PHP event system that was built to be used with the various Doctrine projects.

name: Persistence
description: The Doctrine Persistence project is a set of shared interfaces and functionality that the different Doctrine object mappers share.

name: Reflection
description: The Doctrine Reflection project is a simple library used by the various Doctrine projects which adds some additional functionality on top of the reflection functionality that comes with PHP. It allows you to get the reflection information about classes, methods and properties statically.

name: Coding Standard
description: The Doctrine Coding Standard is a set of PHPCS rules applied to all Doctrine projects.

name: Doctrine1 ORM
description: PHP 5 Doctrine1 Object Relational Mapper (ORM)

name: Instantiator
description: A small, lightweight utility to instantiate objects in PHP without invoking their constructors

name: RST Parser
description: PHP library to parse reStructuredText documents and generate HTML or LaTeX documents.

name: CouchDB Client
description: CouchDB Client

name: Skeleton Mapper
description: The Doctrine SkeletonMapper is a skeleton object mapper where you are 100% responsible for implementing the guts of the persistence operations. This means you write plain old PHP code for the data repositories, object repositories, object hydrators and object persisters.

name: DoctrineBundle
description: Symfony DoctrineBundle

name: Doctrine Cache Bundle
description: Symfony Bundle for Doctrine Cache

name: Doctrine Migrations Bundle
description: Symfony DoctrineMigrationsBundle

name: Doctrine MongoDB Bundle
description: Symfony2 Doctrine MongoDB Bundle

name: DoctrineORMModule
description: Zend Framework Module that provides Doctrine ORM functionality
